headline: Prudential (NYSE:PRU) Surprises With Q3 Sales
summary: Financial services giant Prudential Financial (NYSE:PRU) beat Wall Street’s revenue expectations in Q3 CY2025, but sales fell by 16.7% year on year to $16.24 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $4.26 per share was 14.5% above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: Prudential Financial, Inc. Announces Third Quarter 2025 Results
summary: NEWARK, N.J., October 29, 2025--Prudential Financial, Inc. (NYSE: PRU) today reported third quarter results.
